description: SLANG Worldwide Inc. operates as a cannabis consumer packaged goods company in Canada and the United States. It owns, licenses, and/or markets 10 brands which serve flower, inhalable concentrate, and ingestible. SLANG Worldwide Inc. has a strategic partnership with Trulieve Cannabis Corp. to supply branded cannabis products in Massachusetts. The company was formerly known as Fire Cannabis Inc. and changed its name to SLANG Worldwide Inc. in November 2018. SLANG Worldwide Inc. was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
